title: San Francisco/Fisherman's Wharf
name: North Point Shopping Center
directions: between Mason St and Powell St
content: Less touristy, and set back a few blocks from the actual Wharf, this shopping center contains 15 shops, including a Safeway supermarket, Walgreens drug store, GNC, and Radio Shack, as well as services such as ATMs and 24 Hour Fitness center.
